00:03:45.880 --> 00:03:48.400 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to spend just
a moment elaborating

00:03:48.400 --> 00:03:50.680 align:middle line:90%
on the imagery of Quan Yin.

00:03:50.680 --> 00:03:54.790 align:middle line:84%
As an art historian, I'm always
looking for the ultimate image

00:03:54.790 --> 00:03:56.710 align:middle line:84%
to share with you
and then trying

00:03:56.710 --> 00:03:59.757 align:middle line:84%
to connect various
traditions from the Buddhist,

00:03:59.757 --> 00:04:01.840 align:middle line:84%
to the Christian, to the
Egyptian, to the Tibetan,

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:03.790 align:middle line:84%
to the Mayan, all
across the world,

00:04:03.790 --> 00:04:06.820 align:middle line:84%
looking how they
share a similar story.

00:04:06.820 --> 00:04:09.880 align:middle line:84%
So in this image here, we
see Quan Yin holding a child.

00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:12.280 align:middle line:90%
She's a goddess of compassion.

00:04:12.280 --> 00:04:15.560 align:middle line:84%
Also, some say she's a
goddess of childbirth as well.

00:04:15.560 --> 00:04:17.779 align:middle line:84%
And so in China
and in Japan, you

00:04:17.779 --> 00:04:20.410 align:middle line:84%
will find these wonderful
images of Quan Yin.

00:04:20.410 --> 00:04:21.910 align:middle line:90%
She's also called Chenrezig.

00:04:21.910 --> 00:04:23.950 align:middle line:90%
She's called Avalokitesvara.

00:04:23.950 --> 00:04:26.590 align:middle line:84%
And she is holding
this child in her arms,

00:04:26.590 --> 00:04:29.410 align:middle line:84%
cuddling it just
like the Virgin Mary.

00:04:29.410 --> 00:04:31.810 align:middle line:90%
Exactly like the Virgin Mary.

00:04:31.810 --> 00:04:33.790 align:middle line:84%
But what a lot of
people don't appreciate

00:04:33.790 --> 00:04:36.790 align:middle line:84%
is that the imagery
of Quan Yin actually

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:39.712 align:middle line:84%
were derived from the
images of the Virgin Mary.

00:04:39.712 --> 00:04:41.170 align:middle line:84%
Around the third
or fourth century,

00:04:41.170 --> 00:04:44.320 align:middle line:84%
the earliest Christians high
tailed it out of Jerusalem,

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:46.840 align:middle line:84%
and hit the Silk Road,
and went to Tibet,

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:49.300 align:middle line:84%
and went to China in
these areas bringing

00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:50.800 align:middle line:90%
Christianity with them.

00:04:50.800 --> 00:04:53.020 align:middle line:84%
And along with them, they
brought their artwork.

00:04:53.020 --> 00:04:55.030 align:middle line:84%
So here, we see the
Virgin Mary, obviously

00:04:55.030 --> 00:04:57.400 align:middle line:84%
holding the baby
Jesus in her hand.

00:04:57.400 --> 00:05:01.540 align:middle line:84%
He's got in his hand a blue
orb, maybe a blue apple that

00:05:01.540 --> 00:05:04.180 align:middle line:84%
symbolizes the power
of resurrection,

00:05:04.180 --> 00:05:07.690 align:middle line:84%
which is what ultimately he
came to Earth to teach us.

00:05:07.690 --> 00:05:10.330 align:middle line:84%
And much like the Virgin
Mary-- and this is the key.

00:05:10.330 --> 00:05:12.340 align:middle line:84%
The Chinese Quan
Yin is said to have

00:05:12.340 --> 00:05:17.740 align:middle line:84%
lived a human life of extreme
self-sacrifice and holiness

00:05:17.740 --> 00:05:21.280 align:middle line:84%
before she herself
ascended into heaven

00:05:21.280 --> 00:05:24.590 align:middle line:84%
and became the celestial
goddess of mercy and compassion.

00:05:24.590 --> 00:05:27.520 align:middle line:84%
So at one point, Quan
Yin, like the Virgin Mary,

00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:31.090 align:middle line:84%
had a human incarnation
and went along

00:05:31.090 --> 00:05:34.540 align:middle line:84%
her path of ascension,
her hero's journey,

00:05:34.540 --> 00:05:38.380 align:middle line:84%
and ultimately, ascended to
the pure land of Buddhism

00:05:38.380 --> 00:05:40.870 align:middle line:84%
where she presently
is said to dwell,

00:05:40.870 --> 00:05:44.740 align:middle line:84%
just as Mary is the
first Christian to ascend

00:05:44.740 --> 00:05:48.340 align:middle line:84%
and ascended to the Christian
heaven, a place called Scion.

00:05:48.340 --> 00:05:50.980 align:middle line:84%
So that is a very
important aspect of this.

00:05:50.980 --> 00:05:53.920 align:middle line:84%
And I love the divine
feminine images

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:56.750 align:middle line:84%
that are reflective of
the ascension process.

00:05:56.750 --> 00:05:59.403 align:middle line:90%
Always like to present that.

00:05:59.403 --> 00:06:00.820 align:middle line:84%
And as we look in
the detail here,

00:06:00.820 --> 00:06:03.640 align:middle line:84%
we see this wonderful
image of Quan Yin wearing

00:06:03.640 --> 00:06:07.360 align:middle line:90%
this transparent linen robe.

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:09.890 align:middle line:84%
And as we come in
on this robe here,

00:06:09.890 --> 00:06:12.640 align:middle line:84%
we see that it's actually
covered with orbs of light

00:06:12.640 --> 00:06:14.710 align:middle line:90%
that symbolize stars.

00:06:14.710 --> 00:06:16.930 align:middle line:84%
Don't you just want
to reach in there

00:06:16.930 --> 00:06:19.520 align:middle line:90%
and put that robe on yourself?

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:20.320 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:06:20.320 --> 00:06:22.030 align:middle line:84%
And feel what it
must be like to wear

00:06:22.030 --> 00:06:26.540 align:middle line:84%
it-- be wearing a robe of
stars or a robe of light.

00:06:26.540 --> 00:06:28.090 align:middle line:84%
And that is, of
course, the key image

00:06:28.090 --> 00:06:29.548 align:middle line:84%
in many of the
ascension traditions

00:06:29.548 --> 00:06:32.770 align:middle line:84%
and which is why Mary wears
a row of stars as well.

00:06:32.770 --> 00:06:35.140 align:middle line:84%
Because it indicates
that she is in her star

00:06:35.140 --> 00:06:38.260 align:middle line:84%
body, her light body,
her resurrection body,

00:06:38.260 --> 00:06:39.550 align:middle line:90%
her glory body.

00:06:39.550 --> 00:06:42.475 align:middle line:90%
She's in her ascended frequency.

00:06:42.475 --> 00:06:45.610 align:middle line:84%
In the 17th century, we
find this image of Quan Yin.

00:06:45.610 --> 00:06:49.240 align:middle line:84%
She's sitting on a throne with
two acolytes on either side.

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:52.150 align:middle line:84%
She's sitting on a dragon, just
like the Virgin Mary is always

00:06:52.150 --> 00:06:54.460 align:middle line:84%
shown standing on a
dragon symbolizing

00:06:54.460 --> 00:06:57.100 align:middle line:84%
the earthly forces of
negativity, but also,

00:06:57.100 --> 00:07:00.500 align:middle line:84%
her ability to raise
kundalini as well.

00:07:00.500 --> 00:07:02.710 align:middle line:84%
And again, this
image of Quan Yin

00:07:02.710 --> 00:07:06.250 align:middle line:84%
is entirely derived from
Christian images of Mary

00:07:06.250 --> 00:07:08.980 align:middle line:84%
sitting on the throne,
which a little tip here.

00:07:08.980 --> 00:07:10.220 align:middle line:90%
We won't elaborate on it.

00:07:10.220 --> 00:07:14.110 align:middle line:84%
But we do know that the
throne that Mary sits on

00:07:14.110 --> 00:07:17.935 align:middle line:84%
is called the Throne of
Solomon, the Throne of Wisdom.

00:07:17.935 --> 00:07:20.560 align:middle line:84%
The Essenes called
it the Merkaba.

00:07:20.560 --> 00:07:23.280 align:middle line:84%
So when you're looking at images
with an awakened or enlightened

00:07:23.280 --> 00:07:25.510 align:middle line:84%
eye of Mary sitting
on the throne,

00:07:25.510 --> 00:07:28.780 align:middle line:84%
you know that this
isn't an ordinary throne

00:07:28.780 --> 00:07:30.947 align:middle line:84%
like the Queen of
England would sit on.

00:07:30.947 --> 00:07:32.530 align:middle line:84%
In fact, the Queen
of England's throne

00:07:32.530 --> 00:07:35.230 align:middle line:84%
is actually modeled after
the Throne of Solomon, which

00:07:35.230 --> 00:07:37.270 align:middle line:90%
is actually for the insiders.

00:07:37.270 --> 00:07:38.870 align:middle line:84%
We know that's
actually the Merkaba

00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:40.432 align:middle line:90%
throne, the celestial chariot.

00:07:40.432 --> 00:07:41.890 align:middle line:84%
That's what the
word Merkaba means,

00:07:41.890 --> 00:07:44.500 align:middle line:90%
a celestial throne chariot.

00:07:44.500 --> 00:07:47.350 align:middle line:84%
So this isn't an ordinary
throne that she's sitting on.

00:07:47.350 --> 00:07:51.790 align:middle line:84%
She's actually an exemplar
of the Essene Mystery School

00:07:51.790 --> 00:07:53.800 align:middle line:84%
tradition, which
was all entirely

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:56.320 align:middle line:84%
devoted to attaining
the light body

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:58.930 align:middle line:84%
and ascending on
the Merkaba throne.

00:07:58.930 --> 00:08:01.930 align:middle line:84%
In this image here, it's derived
from the Book of Revelation,

00:08:01.930 --> 00:08:05.640 align:middle line:84%
where John the Revelator,
also an Essene initiate,

00:08:05.640 --> 00:08:08.350 align:middle line:84%
described the holy of holies
of the Celestial City,

00:08:08.350 --> 00:08:11.320 align:middle line:84%
the new Jerusalem,
or Scion, which

00:08:11.320 --> 00:08:14.080 align:middle line:84%
was the target of the
Essene ascension mysteries.

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:16.750 align:middle line:84%
They were trying to
transform their earthly flesh

00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:18.190 align:middle line:84%
into celestial
flesh, so that they

00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:20.740 align:middle line:84%
could dwell in this
Celestial City, which

00:08:20.740 --> 00:08:22.750 align:middle line:90%
they said was inhabited.

00:08:22.750 --> 00:08:26.500 align:middle line:84%
So on the left-hand side, we
see Mary on the Merkaba throne.

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:29.200 align:middle line:84%
We see John the Divine
holding a grail cup.

00:08:29.200 --> 00:08:31.420 align:middle line:10%
And on the right, we
see John the Revelator,

00:08:31.420 --> 00:08:35.110 align:middle line:10%
who is obviously in a state
of ecstasy or in a trance.

00:08:35.110 --> 00:08:36.820 align:middle line:10%
He's got an open book--

00:08:36.820 --> 00:08:38.380 align:middle line:10%
the Book of Revelation.

00:08:38.380 --> 00:08:40.990 align:middle line:84%
And he's gone over the rainbow
bridge of consciousness.

00:08:40.990 --> 00:08:44.020 align:middle line:84%
And he's peering into this
higher dimensional realm.

00:08:44.020 --> 00:08:47.650 align:middle line:10%
He's having a vision or
a visionary experience

00:08:47.650 --> 00:08:50.740 align:middle line:10%
of Scion or the new Jerusalem.

00:08:50.740 --> 00:08:52.540 align:middle line:90%
And it's entirely other worldly.

00:08:52.540 --> 00:08:55.120 align:middle line:84%
It's peopled by
extraordinary beings

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:58.240 align:middle line:90%
and also ascended humans.

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:02.080 align:middle line:10%
So he crosses over the
rainbow, like Dorothy,

00:09:02.080 --> 00:09:06.050 align:middle line:10%
and he describes that
there was a throne of God--

00:09:06.050 --> 00:09:07.720 align:middle line:10%
the Merkaba.

00:09:07.720 --> 00:09:09.970 align:middle line:10%
When the Essenes are ascending
to the throne of God,

00:09:09.970 --> 00:09:12.130 align:middle line:10%
they're ascending
to the Merkaba,

00:09:12.130 --> 00:09:14.950 align:middle line:10%
which exists in this
higher dimensional realm.

00:09:14.950 --> 00:09:16.960 align:middle line:84%
He describes servants
stood in a place

00:09:16.960 --> 00:09:19.900 align:middle line:90%
of perpetual heavenly light.

00:09:19.900 --> 00:09:21.250 align:middle line:90%
Extraordinary description.

00:09:21.250 --> 00:09:22.940 align:middle line:84%
Because in the
"Dead Sea Scrolls,"

00:09:22.940 --> 00:09:25.090 align:middle line:84%
the Essenes were saying
part of their mission

00:09:25.090 --> 00:09:29.050 align:middle line:84%
was to bathe Earth in
perpetual heavenly light.

00:09:29.050 --> 00:09:32.800 align:middle line:84%
Not to necessarily go somewhere,
but to transform Earth

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:35.350 align:middle line:84%
into a planet of righteousness,
a higher frequency

00:09:35.350 --> 00:09:39.340 align:middle line:84%
planet that was bathed in
perpetual heavenly light.

00:09:39.340 --> 00:09:41.500 align:middle line:84%
And just let that roll
through your imagination,

00:09:41.500 --> 00:09:44.110 align:middle line:84%
what it would feel like if our
planet were suddenly bathed

00:09:44.110 --> 00:09:46.140 align:middle line:90%
in perpetual heavenly light.

00:09:46.140 --> 00:09:48.010 align:middle line:10%
It'd be a completely
different world

00:09:48.010 --> 00:09:49.630 align:middle line:10%
that we would be living in.

00:09:49.630 --> 00:09:52.030 align:middle line:10%
And so as John goes
over the rainbow,

00:09:52.030 --> 00:09:55.570 align:middle line:10%
he sees Christ enthroned
on the Merkaba,

00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:58.840 align:middle line:10%
on the celestial throne
chariot with various beings--

00:09:58.840 --> 00:10:00.490 align:middle line:10%
saintly beings, guitar players.

00:10:00.490 --> 00:10:01.700 align:middle line:90%
I'm sure it's Jimmy Page.

00:10:01.700 --> 00:10:02.560 align:middle line:90%
It's Jimi Hendrix.

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:03.890 align:middle line:90%
It's gotta be, right?

00:10:03.890 --> 00:10:07.150 align:middle line:84%
Eddie Van Halen, all with
their guitars in their hand.

00:10:07.150 --> 00:10:08.123 align:middle line:90%
They're rocking out.

00:10:08.123 --> 00:10:09.790 align:middle line:84%
Because they're at
the throne of Christ.

00:10:09.790 --> 00:10:12.380 align:middle line:84%
They've completed their
earthly ascension cycle.

00:10:12.380 --> 00:10:13.600 align:middle line:90%
They're over the rainbow.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:16.840 align:middle line:84%
And they are now in
the celestial Zion.

00:10:16.840 --> 00:10:20.350 align:middle line:84%
And so John in this image,
very much like you and I,

00:10:20.350 --> 00:10:23.740 align:middle line:84%
are actually present
in that throne.

00:10:23.740 --> 00:10:25.540 align:middle line:84%
We're looking at
this image of Christ.

00:10:25.540 --> 00:10:26.500 align:middle line:90%
We're tapping into it.

00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:29.090 align:middle line:84%
But Christ is also
looking back at us.

00:10:29.090 --> 00:10:31.210 align:middle line:84%
And I know that sounds
a little bit nuts,

00:10:31.210 --> 00:10:34.642 align:middle line:84%
but we're going to explain
how and why that is possible.

00:10:34.642 --> 00:10:36.850 align:middle line:84%
As the Book of Hebrews says--
and the Book of Hebrews

00:10:36.850 --> 00:10:40.540 align:middle line:90%
is an Essene ascension manual.

00:10:40.540 --> 00:10:43.030 align:middle line:84%
It was meant to be rehearsed
over and over again.

00:10:43.030 --> 00:10:44.980 align:middle line:84%
The Essenes, like
later the Cathars,

00:10:44.980 --> 00:10:48.400 align:middle line:84%
would use these texts
as guided visualizations

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:51.370 align:middle line:84%
so that they could
concretize the ascension

00:10:51.370 --> 00:10:53.500 align:middle line:84%
journey in their
minds, so that they

00:10:53.500 --> 00:10:55.450 align:middle line:84%
knew exactly what
was going to happen

00:10:55.450 --> 00:10:57.490 align:middle line:90%
in their afterlife journey.

00:10:57.490 --> 00:10:58.480 align:middle line:90%
They had modeled it.

00:10:58.480 --> 00:11:00.060 align:middle line:84%
They had wired
their brain for it.

00:11:00.060 --> 00:11:01.960 align:middle line:84%
They had connected
their soul to it.

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:05.680 align:middle line:84%
So it was like me leaving this
room, walking out of the hotel,

00:11:05.680 --> 00:11:09.370 align:middle line:84%
catching the shuttle, going over
to LAX, and flying home, right?

00:11:09.370 --> 00:11:12.670 align:middle line:84%
That is essentially-- they would
rehearse the heavenly journey

00:11:12.670 --> 00:11:17.110 align:middle line:84%
over and over and over again,
until they absolutely embodied

00:11:17.110 --> 00:11:18.280 align:middle line:90%
it.

00:11:18.280 --> 00:11:21.790 align:middle line:84%
And they knew that once they
completed their ascension,

00:11:21.790 --> 00:11:25.180 align:middle line:84%
that they would go to this
place that was populated by,

00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:28.870 align:middle line:84%
as Hebrews says, innumerable
company of angels

00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:32.560 align:middle line:90%
and just humans made perfect.

00:11:32.560 --> 00:11:36.610 align:middle line:90%
Just humans made perfect.

00:11:36.610 --> 00:11:38.140 align:middle line:90%
Well, who are these people?

00:11:38.140 --> 00:11:39.940 align:middle line:90%
And how did they become perfect?

00:11:39.940 --> 00:11:41.113 align:middle line:90%
What does this mean?

00:11:41.113 --> 00:11:43.030 align:middle line:84%
Well, when you look up
the meaning of the word

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:46.950 align:middle line:84%
"just," it means upright,
righteous, and balanced.

00:11:46.950 --> 00:11:49.060 align:middle line:84%
And just in this case
doesn't mean they're

00:11:49.060 --> 00:11:50.840 align:middle line:90%
only humans made perfect.

00:11:50.840 --> 00:11:51.640 align:middle line:90%
They're just.

00:11:51.640 --> 00:11:52.930 align:middle line:90%
They're righteous.

00:11:52.930 --> 00:11:54.190 align:middle line:90%
They're holy people.

00:11:54.190 --> 00:11:56.980 align:middle line:84%
They're humans, which means
they're a member of the species

00:11:56.980 --> 00:11:58.118 align:middle line:90%
Homo sapien.

00:11:58.118 --> 00:11:59.410 align:middle line:90%
And here's a punchline for you.

00:11:59.410 --> 00:12:02.650 align:middle line:84%
They're not animal,
divine, or machine,

00:12:02.650 --> 00:12:05.290 align:middle line:84%
which we won't get into
the AI aspect of this.

00:12:05.290 --> 00:12:08.680 align:middle line:90%
But can a transhuman ascend?

00:12:08.680 --> 00:12:12.740 align:middle line:84%
According to this,
no, you cannot.

00:12:12.740 --> 00:12:15.890 align:middle line:84%
They're made, meaning
they're shaped or formed.

00:12:15.890 --> 00:12:18.710 align:middle line:84%
And they're perfect,
meaning they're complete.

00:12:18.710 --> 00:12:19.970 align:middle line:90%
They're fully developed.

00:12:19.970 --> 00:12:20.870 align:middle line:90%
They're whole.

00:12:20.870 --> 00:12:21.790 align:middle line:90%
They're holy.

00:12:21.790 --> 00:12:24.200 align:middle line:90%
They're 360.

00:12:24.200 --> 00:12:27.650 align:middle line:84%
And they're effectively what
I would term "I am-plus."

00:12:27.650 --> 00:12:29.700 align:middle line:90%
They are more than human.

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:33.500 align:middle line:84%
They are just
humans made perfect.

00:12:33.500 --> 00:12:35.450 align:middle line:84%
And in the Essene
tradition, this

00:12:35.450 --> 00:12:38.780 align:middle line:84%
is our goal, is to become
more whole, more holy, more

00:12:38.780 --> 00:12:40.910 align:middle line:90%
complete, and indeed, perfect.

00:12:40.910 --> 00:12:44.330 align:middle line:84%
And I use the term 360,
because that comes from a text

00:12:44.330 --> 00:12:46.320 align:middle line:90%
that the Essenes actually read.

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:48.110 align:middle line:84%
It's called the
"Epic of Gilgamesh."

00:12:48.110 --> 00:12:51.610 align:middle line:84%
It's the world's
second oldest story.

00:12:51.610 --> 00:12:53.820 align:middle line:84%
And essentially, it's
an ascension story

00:12:53.820 --> 00:12:57.110 align:middle line:84%
where an Iraqi king
named Gilgamesh

00:12:57.110 --> 00:12:58.580 align:middle line:90%
is on his ascension path.

00:12:58.580 --> 00:13:01.880 align:middle line:84%
And he gets a lucky break when
the goddess Inanna comes to him

00:13:01.880 --> 00:13:07.100 align:middle line:84%
and tells him, brother, you're
2/3 divine and 1/3 human.

00:13:07.100 --> 00:13:09.470 align:middle line:84%
And if you try to go through
the gate of the gods--

00:13:09.470 --> 00:13:13.227 align:middle line:84%
which is his attempt in the
"Epic of Gilgamesh--" as 2/3

00:13:13.227 --> 00:13:14.810 align:middle line:84%
human and 1/3 divine,
it's going to be

00:13:14.810 --> 00:13:15.977 align:middle line:90%
like walking into a blender.

00:13:15.977 --> 00:13:18.290 align:middle line:84%
You're going to get
your feathers ruffled.

00:13:18.290 --> 00:13:21.350 align:middle line:84%
So what you want to do before
you go through that gate

00:13:21.350 --> 00:13:27.410 align:middle line:84%
is to clean up your act, to go
from 2/3 divine and 1/3 human

00:13:27.410 --> 00:13:29.160 align:middle line:90%
to 360.

00:13:29.160 --> 00:13:31.400 align:middle line:84%
Now, if divinity is
symbolized by a circle--

00:13:31.400 --> 00:13:34.070 align:middle line:90%
and a circle is 360 degrees.

00:13:34.070 --> 00:13:37.010 align:middle line:84%
If we're 2/3 human
and 1/3 divine,

00:13:37.010 --> 00:13:41.680 align:middle line:84%
that means we start out
at about 240 out of 360.

00:13:41.680 --> 00:13:45.520 align:middle line:84%
And our quest then is to move
the needle to become 360.

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:49.560 align:middle line:84%
And the way we do that is by
changing what we're doing,

00:13:49.560 --> 00:13:50.360 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:13:50.360 --> 00:13:52.310 align:middle line:84%
This was the message
to Gilgamesh.

00:13:52.310 --> 00:13:54.847 align:middle line:84%
But if he keeps doing the
same things that he's doing,

00:13:54.847 --> 00:13:56.930 align:middle line:84%
he's not going to be able
to get through the gate.

00:13:56.930 --> 00:13:59.690 align:middle line:84%
So all of us are charged in
our own personal experience

00:13:59.690 --> 00:14:04.760 align:middle line:84%
to figure out, how can we
go from 240, 280, 290, 320,

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:06.050 align:middle line:90%
to 360?

00:14:06.050 --> 00:14:07.550 align:middle line:84%
And part of what
we have to do is

00:14:07.550 --> 00:14:12.770 align:middle line:84%
to begin to connect with a
vision of what our life will

00:14:12.770 --> 00:14:15.830 align:middle line:90%
be like when we are at 360.

00:14:15.830 --> 00:14:18.770 align:middle line:84%
And for many of us, it's going
to be individually specific.

00:14:18.770 --> 00:14:22.100 align:middle line:84%
But there are also keys
that we get from ancient art

00:14:22.100 --> 00:14:24.830 align:middle line:84%
and traditions that tells
us what a fully functioning

00:14:24.830 --> 00:14:27.690 align:middle line:90%
human being actually can do.

00:14:27.690 --> 00:14:30.830 align:middle line:84%
And one of the things a fully
functioning human being can do

00:14:30.830 --> 00:14:34.820 align:middle line:84%
is adopt a consciousness
similar to that of Christ

00:14:34.820 --> 00:14:40.410 align:middle line:84%
and to have superhuman
powers, ascension powers.

00:14:40.410 --> 00:14:42.510 align:middle line:84%
What we're looking at
here is a correspondence

00:14:42.510 --> 00:14:45.910 align:middle line:84%
between the Buddhist tradition
and the Christian tradition.

00:14:45.910 --> 00:14:49.770 align:middle line:84%
This is the Dalai Lama looking
up, visualizing his connection

00:14:49.770 --> 00:14:51.540 align:middle line:90%
with Quan Yin.

00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:54.660 align:middle line:84%
So he's sitting in a state of
visualization or meditation,

00:14:54.660 --> 00:14:57.660 align:middle line:84%
deep gamma, perhaps,
looking up at this orb

00:14:57.660 --> 00:15:01.350 align:middle line:84%
of rainbow-colored light,
just exactly like John

00:15:01.350 --> 00:15:03.480 align:middle line:84%
the Revelator is,
crossing over the rainbow

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:06.660 align:middle line:84%
bridge of consciousness and
having a vision of Christ

00:15:06.660 --> 00:15:08.200 align:middle line:90%
in the very same rainbow.

00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:10.440 align:middle line:90%
It's the exact same scene.

00:15:10.440 --> 00:15:13.320 align:middle line:84%
And what this illustrates for
us is one form of practice

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:15.330 align:middle line:84%
for awakening to
one's true nature

00:15:15.330 --> 00:15:18.570 align:middle line:84%
in Buddhism that's highly
respected by Buddhists,

00:15:18.570 --> 00:15:22.620 align:middle line:84%
is connecting with the qualities
of an enlightened being,

00:15:22.620 --> 00:15:26.940 align:middle line:84%
one who is already awake
and then modeling what

00:15:26.940 --> 00:15:31.470 align:middle line:84%
they are doing as an
example and an inspiration.

00:15:31.470 --> 00:15:33.360 align:middle line:84%
So this is what this
Dalai Lama is doing.

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:38.250 align:middle line:84%
He is actually visualizing Quan
Yin in her ascended rainbow

00:15:38.250 --> 00:15:39.360 align:middle line:90%
light body.

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:43.020 align:middle line:10%
And he's contemplating,
meditating, and reflecting on,

00:15:43.020 --> 00:15:46.950 align:middle line:10%
what is it that Quan Yin
has in her ascended state

00:15:46.950 --> 00:15:48.010 align:middle line:10%
that I don't have?

00:15:48.010 --> 00:15:49.650 align:middle line:10%
She's a 360 being.

00:15:49.650 --> 00:15:51.520 align:middle line:90%
She is "I am-plus."

00:15:51.520 --> 00:15:52.320 align:middle line:90%
He isn't.

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:55.020 align:middle line:90%
He's trying to get on this path.

00:15:55.020 --> 00:15:59.160 align:middle line:84%
And one key here is that
whenever the Dalai Lamas were

00:15:59.160 --> 00:16:02.940 align:middle line:84%
taught how to attain this
elevated state of being,

00:16:02.940 --> 00:16:06.540 align:middle line:84%
this rainbow light body, they
were never taught with texts.

00:16:06.540 --> 00:16:08.940 align:middle line:84%
There are no books you can
read about how to attain

00:16:08.940 --> 00:16:11.010 align:middle line:90%
your rainbow light body.

00:16:11.010 --> 00:16:13.950 align:middle line:84%
The Dalai Lamas, instead, would
be taken out behind the Potala

00:16:13.950 --> 00:16:17.970 align:middle line:84%
Palace when they were in Tibet
into a circular room that

00:16:17.970 --> 00:16:21.570 align:middle line:84%
is 360 degrees
covered with images.

00:16:21.570 --> 00:16:26.520 align:middle line:84%
And they were taught the rainbow
light body through images.

00:16:26.520 --> 00:16:29.820 align:middle line:84%
This is because the higher
dimensional rainbow light

00:16:29.820 --> 00:16:34.110 align:middle line:84%
body beings could manifest
through those images

00:16:34.110 --> 00:16:36.180 align:middle line:84%
and connect with the
consciousness of the Dalai

00:16:36.180 --> 00:16:39.210 align:middle line:84%
Lamas and perhaps give
them downloads or transmit

00:16:39.210 --> 00:16:41.050 align:middle line:90%
frequencies to them.

00:16:41.050 --> 00:16:47.130 align:middle line:84%
So this is why my emphasis is
on the art of living ascension.

00:16:47.130 --> 00:16:49.200 align:middle line:84%
Because it is the
art, the image that

00:16:49.200 --> 00:16:52.170 align:middle line:84%
shows us the way as the
"Gnostic Gospels" say.

00:16:52.170 --> 00:16:55.650 align:middle line:84%
And there's a science, a sacred
science behind all of this

00:16:55.650 --> 00:16:59.910 align:middle line:84%
that we're trying to recover
and share in the modern world.

00:16:59.910 --> 00:17:02.420 align:middle line:84%
In his book, the teaching
on Chenrezig sadhana,

00:17:02.420 --> 00:17:04.589 align:middle line:84%
Kalu Rinpoche
said, "One does not

00:17:04.589 --> 00:17:07.920 align:middle line:84%
think of the deity's body--"
in this case, Quan Yin--

00:17:07.920 --> 00:17:10.500 align:middle line:84%
"as solid or material
made of flesh and blood

00:17:10.500 --> 00:17:15.180 align:middle line:84%
like one's ordinary body or made
of metal or stone like an idol.

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:18.060 align:middle line:84%
One thinks of it
as appearance that

00:17:18.060 --> 00:17:21.210 align:middle line:84%
is inseparable from
emptiness like a rainbow

00:17:21.210 --> 00:17:24.119 align:middle line:84%
or like a reflection
in a mirror."

00:17:24.119 --> 00:17:25.829 align:middle line:84%
And that is one of
the key concepts here

00:17:25.829 --> 00:17:29.910 align:middle line:84%
is that we are instructed
to look at Quan Yin

00:17:29.910 --> 00:17:32.700 align:middle line:84%
as if we are
looking in a mirror.

00:17:32.700 --> 00:17:36.510 align:middle line:84%
And then we are to mirror
what we are seeing, feeling,

00:17:36.510 --> 00:17:39.480 align:middle line:90%
or otherwise experiencing.

00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:42.030 align:middle line:84%
The image that's visualized
in this meditation

00:17:42.030 --> 00:17:44.070 align:middle line:84%
practice-- and this is
a meditation practice

00:17:44.070 --> 00:17:45.620 align:middle line:90%
that I'm offering here.

00:17:45.620 --> 00:17:47.880 align:middle line:84%
This is another
tool in your kit.

00:17:47.880 --> 00:17:49.740 align:middle line:84%
No matter what
else you're doing--

00:17:49.740 --> 00:17:53.790 align:middle line:84%
yoga, meditation,
fasting, any other tool

00:17:53.790 --> 00:17:56.310 align:middle line:84%
that you're using
to cleanse, purify,

00:17:56.310 --> 00:18:00.260 align:middle line:84%
raise your frequency-- this
is another tool for your kit.

00:18:00.260 --> 00:18:02.970 align:middle line:84%
And so the image that's
visualized in the meditation

00:18:02.970 --> 00:18:05.340 align:middle line:84%
practice is not
a real person who

00:18:05.340 --> 00:18:08.280 align:middle line:84%
happens to be perfect
in every imaginable way.

00:18:08.280 --> 00:18:10.050 align:middle line:90%
It's an image.

00:18:10.050 --> 00:18:12.240 align:middle line:84%
It's an image and
an imaginary form

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.680 align:middle line:84%
with certain
wonderful qualities.

00:18:13.680 --> 00:18:16.307 align:middle line:84%
She radiates
rainbow color light.

00:18:16.307 --> 00:18:18.390 align:middle line:84%
And if she were to manifest
in this room right now

00:18:18.390 --> 00:18:20.323 align:middle line:84%
and it was dark, she
would be glowing.

00:18:20.323 --> 00:18:21.240 align:middle line:90%
She would be luminous.

00:18:21.240 --> 00:18:25.513 align:middle line:84%
She'd be radiant, be
literally a being of light.

00:18:25.513 --> 00:18:27.180 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm encouraging
you to do here--

00:18:27.180 --> 00:18:28.530 align:middle line:84%
and maybe you'll take
out your cell phone,

00:18:28.530 --> 00:18:29.670 align:middle line:90%
take a quick photo--

00:18:29.670 --> 00:18:31.950 align:middle line:84%
is that this is one
way that you can

00:18:31.950 --> 00:18:37.950 align:middle line:84%
connect with this vibration of
Quan Yin is through the image.

00:18:37.950 --> 00:18:40.140 align:middle line:84%
Several years ago, they
said the average person

00:18:40.140 --> 00:18:44.310 align:middle line:84%
looks at their cell
phone 200 times a day.

00:18:44.310 --> 00:18:46.150 align:middle line:90%
It's probably a lot more now.

00:18:46.150 --> 00:18:48.720 align:middle line:84%
And so just imagine
if half of that time,

00:18:48.720 --> 00:18:50.370 align:middle line:84%
you're looking at
your starting screen

00:18:50.370 --> 00:18:51.990 align:middle line:90%
on your phone or your computer.

00:18:51.990 --> 00:18:54.390 align:middle line:84%
And you're connecting
with Quan Yin,

00:18:54.390 --> 00:18:57.048 align:middle line:84%
just taking that moment
to reflect on that.

00:18:57.048 --> 00:18:58.590 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I had a
medical doctor that's

00:18:58.590 --> 00:18:59.632 align:middle line:90%
known me for a long time.

00:18:59.632 --> 00:19:02.190 align:middle line:84%
She said, boy, you've really
changed in the past 10 years

00:19:02.190 --> 00:19:03.540 align:middle line:90%
since I've known you.

00:19:03.540 --> 00:19:05.790 align:middle line:90%
And you've grown a lot lighter.

00:19:05.790 --> 00:19:07.405 align:middle line:90%
And how are you doing that?

00:19:07.405 --> 00:19:08.530 align:middle line:90%
I said, well, I don't know.

00:19:08.530 --> 00:19:11.820 align:middle line:84%
I've just spent hours every day
staring at my computer screen,

00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:13.800 align:middle line:90%
working on presentations.

00:19:13.800 --> 00:19:15.940 align:middle line:84%
And I'm always connecting
with these beings.

00:19:15.940 --> 00:19:19.280 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps that's-- what I'm
saying to you is working for me.

00:19:19.280 --> 00:19:20.080 align:middle line:90%
I hope so.

00:19:20.080 --> 00:19:22.560 align:middle line:84%
Because I will continue
to do it, right?

00:19:22.560 --> 00:19:25.200 align:middle line:84%
So what I'm wanting
to suggest here

00:19:25.200 --> 00:19:28.950 align:middle line:84%
is that we can connect with
these higher dimensional beings

00:19:28.950 --> 00:19:30.480 align:middle line:90%
through the image.

