00:22:20.270 --> 00:22:23.390 align:middle line:84%
And one thing that happened in
my path that I love to share

00:22:23.390 --> 00:22:25.700 align:middle line:84%
and I'm glad to have an
opportunity to do so today

00:22:25.700 --> 00:22:30.590 align:middle line:84%
is back in 2003, it was one
of my first visits to Egypt.

00:22:30.590 --> 00:22:33.260 align:middle line:90%
I'm on a cruise ship in Luxor.

00:22:33.260 --> 00:22:35.510 align:middle line:84%
And I'm just-- had this
mind-blowing experience

00:22:35.510 --> 00:22:36.680 align:middle line:90%
in Egypt already.

00:22:36.680 --> 00:22:39.020 align:middle line:84%
The cruise director calls
me on the phone and says,

00:22:39.020 --> 00:22:40.840 align:middle line:84%
we're ready for the
belly dancer now.

00:22:40.840 --> 00:22:41.840 align:middle line:90%
Why don't you come down?

00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:43.340 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, oh,
man, I'm so tired.

00:22:43.340 --> 00:22:45.400 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to go see
a belly dancer tonight.

00:22:45.400 --> 00:22:47.910 align:middle line:84%
The cruise guy called
me three times.

00:22:47.910 --> 00:22:51.650 align:middle line:84%
And finally, I'm like, OK, I'll
come watch the belly dancer.

00:22:51.650 --> 00:22:52.910 align:middle line:90%
And so I go into the lounge.

00:22:52.910 --> 00:22:54.350 align:middle line:84%
And here, it's not
a belly dancer.

00:22:54.350 --> 00:22:56.320 align:middle line:90%
It's a whirling dervish dancer.

00:22:56.320 --> 00:22:59.420 align:middle line:84%
And he's performing an
800-year-old mystic Islamic

00:22:59.420 --> 00:23:01.070 align:middle line:90%
dance where he takes his skirt.

00:23:01.070 --> 00:23:04.370 align:middle line:84%
He's spinning in place,
going into a deep state

00:23:04.370 --> 00:23:05.660 align:middle line:90%
of meditation.

00:23:05.660 --> 00:23:07.190 align:middle line:90%
And he's spinning.

00:23:07.190 --> 00:23:11.180 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, I hear this
crashing sound on the floor,

00:23:11.180 --> 00:23:13.040 align:middle line:90%
and it's my jaw.

00:23:13.040 --> 00:23:17.450 align:middle line:84%
Because I'm thinking, that's
Elijah in the whirlwind.

00:23:17.450 --> 00:23:19.370 align:middle line:84%
That's all of these
biblical stories

00:23:19.370 --> 00:23:21.530 align:middle line:84%
of Ezekiel going
up into the heavens

00:23:21.530 --> 00:23:24.470 align:middle line:84%
in a spinning
wheel of some kind.

00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:28.118 align:middle line:84%
And he's turning his
body into this Merkaba.

00:23:28.118 --> 00:23:29.660 align:middle line:84%
This is what he's
demonstrating here.

00:23:29.660 --> 00:23:31.190 align:middle line:90%
It's very clear.

00:23:31.190 --> 00:23:33.950 align:middle line:10%
And then it gets
even more incredible

00:23:33.950 --> 00:23:35.480 align:middle line:10%
when he takes out
his second skirt

00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:38.930 align:middle line:10%
and starts spinning it in
a counterclockwise fashion.

00:23:38.930 --> 00:23:42.840 align:middle line:84%
And I realize, that's
the shape of a wormhole.

00:23:42.840 --> 00:23:47.450 align:middle line:84%
He has just turned his
body into a wormhole, which

00:23:47.450 --> 00:23:49.860 align:middle line:90%
is absolutely mind blowing.

00:23:49.860 --> 00:23:53.060 align:middle line:84%
And then afterword,
what happens is

00:23:53.060 --> 00:23:55.670 align:middle line:84%
that his assistant
comes out, provides him

00:23:55.670 --> 00:23:57.080 align:middle line:90%
with this linen shroud.

00:23:57.080 --> 00:23:59.840 align:middle line:84%
He takes his second skirt,
wraps it into a bundle,

00:23:59.840 --> 00:24:02.540 align:middle line:84%
and then they wrap the linen
shroud around the bundle.

00:24:02.540 --> 00:24:04.450 align:middle line:90%
And they feed it milk.

00:24:04.450 --> 00:24:07.460 align:middle line:84%
And it's like, what's
the message for us?

00:24:07.460 --> 00:24:10.070 align:middle line:84%
Well, part of the
message is, where did you

00:24:10.070 --> 00:24:13.200 align:middle line:90%
