00:24:13.200 --> 00:24:14.000 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:16.400 align:middle line:84%
And when you decide you're
going to leave here,

00:24:16.400 --> 00:24:18.500 align:middle line:90%
