00:24:18.500 --> 00:24:21.190 align:middle line:84%
And how are you
going to get there?

00:24:21.190 --> 00:24:22.220 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:24:22.220 --> 00:24:25.850 align:middle line:84%
And the answer is we
come through wormholes.

00:24:25.850 --> 00:24:28.280 align:middle line:84%
And so in the Sufi
tradition, which

00:24:28.280 --> 00:24:32.030 align:middle line:84%
is the mystic Islamic
tradition going back 800 years,

00:24:32.030 --> 00:24:33.800 align:middle line:84%
they have this
incredible tradition

00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:38.210 align:middle line:84%
started by the poet Rumi
who is a Islamic mystic

00:24:38.210 --> 00:24:42.080 align:middle line:84%
of these whirling dervishes,
who go into these trances

00:24:42.080 --> 00:24:44.060 align:middle line:90%
