00:24:44.060 --> 00:24:47.070 align:middle line:84%
just scarves and
wrappings around them.

00:24:47.070 --> 00:24:49.700 align:middle line:84%
And it's very clear that
what we're looking at

00:24:49.700 --> 00:24:51.886 align:middle line:90%
