00:24:51.886 --> 00:24:53.550 align:middle line:90%
>> Activating the Merkaba.

00:24:53.550 --> 00:24:56.130 align:middle line:84%
>> Activating the Merkaba,
the rainbow light body.

00:24:56.130 --> 00:24:57.330 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:24:57.330 --> 00:25:00.780 align:middle line:84%
So we've just crossed over
from the Christian tradition

00:25:00.780 --> 00:25:03.720 align:middle line:84%
