tradition into mystic Islam.

00:25:03.720 --> 00:25:05.790 align:middle line:84%
And they're all
telling the same thing.

00:25:05.790 --> 00:25:08.190 align:middle line:84%
Our body is capable
of being transformed

00:25:08.190 --> 00:25:10.800 align:middle line:90%
