00:25:10.800 --> 00:25:13.170 align:middle line:84%
And we need to learn
how to do that.

00:25:13.170 --> 00:25:15.640 align:middle line:84%
And they've been encoding
it in their sacred art

00:25:15.640 --> 00:25:19.890 align:middle line:84%
and in the Islamic tradition
and within a sacred dance.

00:25:19.890 --> 00:25:22.650 align:middle line:84%
This rainbow light
body is what we

00:25:22.650 --> 00:25:26.970 align:middle line:84%
