with on our ascension path.

00:25:26.970 --> 00:25:29.760 align:middle line:84%
It is our true nature,
according to the Buddhists.

00:25:29.760 --> 00:25:31.530 align:middle line:90%
It's who we truly are.

00:25:31.530 --> 00:25:34.680 align:middle line:84%
Deep inside you is
this being of light.

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:38.280 align:middle line:84%
The rainbow light body
isn't something you go get.

00:25:38.280 --> 00:25:40.770 align:middle line:84%
It's something that
you already are,

00:25:40.770 --> 00:25:44.880 align:middle line:84%
that is covered over
by misperceptions,

00:25:44.880 --> 00:25:48.420 align:middle line:84%
by negative thought forms,
by culture that says,

00:25:48.420 --> 00:25:51.780 align:middle line:90%
