00:25:51.780 --> 00:25:53.400 align:middle line:84%
And the fact of
the matter is, is

00:25:53.400 --> 00:25:54.870 align:middle line:84%
that all of these
sacred traditions

00:25:54.870 --> 00:25:58.680 align:middle line:84%
tell us that this
is who we truly are,

00:25:58.680 --> 00:26:01.690 align:middle line:84%
this rainbow light
body being within us.

00:26:01.690 --> 00:26:03.360 align:middle line:90%
This is Padmasambhava.

00:26:03.360 --> 00:26:05.910 align:middle line:84%
He's a Tibetan guru,
came from India to Tibet

00:26:05.910 --> 00:26:06.780 align:middle line:90%
