the "Hutchinson Collection"

00:38:55.043 --> 00:38:56.085 align:middle line:10%
at Ohio State University.

00:38:56.085 --> 00:38:58.930 align:middle line:10%
It's, I think, one of the
most remarkable images

00:38:58.930 --> 00:39:00.970 align:middle line:10%
of Padmasambhava and
the rainbow light body.

00:39:00.970 --> 00:39:03.280 align:middle line:84%
Because we clearly
see the blue pearl

00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:07.270 align:middle line:84%
or the blue apple in the
third eye in the pineal gland.

00:39:07.270 --> 00:39:10.330 align:middle line:10%
And meditating on this image
while chanting, om mani padme

00:39:10.330 --> 00:39:13.810 align:middle line:10%
hum calls in those
divine blessings,

00:39:13.810 --> 00:39:17.740 align:middle line:10%
and connects you even more
deeply with Padmasambhava,

00:39:17.740 --> 00:39:20.830 align:middle line:10%
and opens up a channel
for him to assist you

00:39:20.830 --> 00:39:25.985 align:middle line:10%
in awakening and manifesting
your rainbow light body,

00:39:25.985 --> 00:39:29.030 align:middle line:10%
so I love that image.

00:39:29.030 --> 00:39:33.590 align:middle line:84%
And there you see the blue pearl
highlighted in the third eye.

00:39:33.590 --> 00:39:36.760 align:middle line:84%
The pineal gland, of course,
is called the seat of the soul.

00:39:36.760 --> 00:39:37.740 align:middle line:90%
It's thought of as--

00:39:37.740 --> 00:39:42.550 align:middle line:84%
it's a manufacturing plant
of sacred oils, secretions

00:39:42.550 --> 00:39:44.245 align:middle line:84%
that contain the
secrets of transmuting

00:39:44.245 --> 00:39:45.980 align:middle line:90%
the body into light.

00:39:45.980 --> 00:39:49.120 align:middle line:84%
That's why there's the
emphasis on the pineal gland

00:39:49.120 --> 00:39:54.220 align:middle line:84%
and awakening its capability to
transmute our physical flesh.

00:39:54.220 --> 00:39:57.370 align:middle line:84%
You're familiar with this
state of being I'm describing.

00:39:57.370 --> 00:39:59.360 align:middle line:84%
You ever see the movie,
"The Wizard of Oz?"

00:39:59.360 --> 00:40:00.160 align:middle line:90%
Remember?

00:40:00.160 --> 00:40:03.280 align:middle line:90%
Dorothy goes up in a vortex.

00:40:03.280 --> 00:40:05.557 align:middle line:84%
She's in a dream to
begin with, right?

00:40:05.557 --> 00:40:06.640 align:middle line:90%
She goes up in the vortex.

00:40:06.640 --> 00:40:08.680 align:middle line:90%
And she's in a place called Oz.

00:40:08.680 --> 00:40:14.050 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly out of the blue,
comes this orb of light.

00:40:14.050 --> 00:40:15.760 align:middle line:10%
And within this
orb of light, she

00:40:15.760 --> 00:40:20.680 align:middle line:10%
begins to detect this
luminous humanoid figure,

00:40:20.680 --> 00:40:24.610 align:middle line:10%
the good witch, Glinda, who's
wearing a cloak of light.

00:40:24.610 --> 00:40:27.040 align:middle line:10%
She's got a resurrection
or star stick in her hand.

00:40:27.040 --> 00:40:29.140 align:middle line:10%
And she's wearing a crown.

00:40:29.140 --> 00:40:33.160 align:middle line:10%
She is dressed exactly
like Padmasambhava

00:40:33.160 --> 00:40:35.500 align:middle line:10%
in his rainbow light body,
who holds the resurrection

00:40:35.500 --> 00:40:37.660 align:middle line:10%
stick that opens the
gates of heaven and hell.

00:40:37.660 --> 00:40:41.430 align:middle line:10%
His crown, his vajra,
and his heart chakra--

00:40:41.430 --> 00:40:43.340 align:middle line:10%
they're identical.

00:40:43.340 --> 00:40:45.160 align:middle line:84%
In fact, they're
identical in exactly that

00:40:45.160 --> 00:40:46.660 align:middle line:90%
what they're able to do.

00:40:46.660 --> 00:40:51.130 align:middle line:84%
They can phase in between their
physical flesh and blood cells

00:40:51.130 --> 00:40:52.880 align:middle line:90%
and their light body selves.

00:40:52.880 --> 00:40:55.472 align:middle line:90%
And so can you.

00:40:55.472 --> 00:40:57.430 align:middle line:84%
You'll never get me up
on one of those, though,

00:40:57.430 --> 00:40:58.960 align:middle line:90%
is what our culture says.

00:40:58.960 --> 00:41:00.950 align:middle line:84%
And that's the gap
we have to close.

00:41:00.950 --> 00:41:02.590 align:middle line:84%
We have to say,
well, wait a minute.

00:41:02.590 --> 00:41:04.870 align:middle line:90%
Yes, we, in fact, can do this.

00:41:04.870 --> 00:41:07.600 align:middle line:84%
And this is what is reflected
in Buddhist art where they say,

00:41:07.600 --> 00:41:10.810 align:middle line:84%
we're always connected
to our true selves,

00:41:10.810 --> 00:41:13.630 align:middle line:84%
to our pure self, our whole,
holy, and complete self.

00:41:13.630 --> 00:41:16.510 align:middle line:84%
It's always there in
our consciousness.

00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:19.660 align:middle line:84%
This, in fact, comes from
the Dalai Lama secret temple.

00:41:19.660 --> 00:41:23.130 align:middle line:84%
The Rubin Museum in Manhattan
and Chelsea in New York

00:41:23.130 --> 00:41:25.990 align:middle line:84%
actually has a recreation
of that temple.

00:41:25.990 --> 00:41:29.740 align:middle line:84%
Or it's not on display now, but
periodically, it's on display.

00:41:29.740 --> 00:41:32.800 align:middle line:84%
And this is one of those
images that the Dalai Lamas

00:41:32.800 --> 00:41:35.320 align:middle line:84%
would be instructed
in, in this rainbow

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:37.960 align:middle line:84%
bridge that links
our consciousness

00:41:37.960 --> 00:41:40.540 align:middle line:90%
with our true self.

00:41:40.540 --> 00:41:43.280 align:middle line:84%
And it's wonderful,
another example

00:41:43.280 --> 00:41:49.405 align:middle line:84%
of a living image that connects
us with our true selves.

00:41:49.405 --> 00:41:53.092 align:middle line:90%


00:41:53.092 --> 00:41:54.800 align:middle line:84%
Flipping back to the
Christian tradition,

00:41:54.800 --> 00:41:56.765 align:middle line:84%
we find this story of
John the Revelator who

00:41:56.765 --> 00:42:01.010 align:middle line:84%
is visited by an angel who
came down out of heaven,

00:42:01.010 --> 00:42:02.520 align:middle line:90%
says the Book of Revelation.

00:42:02.520 --> 00:42:04.340 align:middle line:10%
The heavens open all
the time in the Bible.

00:42:04.340 --> 00:42:07.723 align:middle line:10%
And I think those are
stargate and wormhole events.

00:42:07.723 --> 00:42:09.140 align:middle line:10%
So this angel comes
out of heaven,

00:42:09.140 --> 00:42:11.780 align:middle line:10%
morphs into a flesh
and blood form

00:42:11.780 --> 00:42:14.180 align:middle line:10%
that can be seen or perceived.

00:42:14.180 --> 00:42:18.460 align:middle line:10%
He's clothed with a cloud and
a rainbow around his head.

00:42:18.460 --> 00:42:20.960 align:middle line:10%
I don't know why, but I'm the
first person in all of history

00:42:20.960 --> 00:42:23.480 align:middle line:10%
to connect the angel that
John the Revelator saw

00:42:23.480 --> 00:42:24.950 align:middle line:10%
with the rainbow
light body beings.

00:42:24.950 --> 00:42:28.430 align:middle line:84%
I think they're the
exact same type of being.

00:42:28.430 --> 00:42:30.290 align:middle line:84%
They're in the same
state of being.

00:42:30.290 --> 00:42:33.320 align:middle line:10%
And he comes out of heaven,
this rainbow angel does.

00:42:33.320 --> 00:42:35.870 align:middle line:10%
And he's got a book
for John to eat.

00:42:35.870 --> 00:42:39.410 align:middle line:84%
Now, I take tremendous
comfort in this story

00:42:39.410 --> 00:42:41.300 align:middle line:84%
of John the Revelator
in this image.

00:42:41.300 --> 00:42:44.510 align:middle line:84%
Because what it tells
me is that I don't

00:42:44.510 --> 00:42:48.330 align:middle line:90%
have to do this all by myself.

00:42:48.330 --> 00:42:49.850 align:middle line:90%
I have my higher self.

00:42:49.850 --> 00:42:52.130 align:middle line:84%
And we could argue that
this rainbow angel is John

00:42:52.130 --> 00:42:53.900 align:middle line:90%
the Revelator's higher self.

00:42:53.900 --> 00:42:58.220 align:middle line:84%
Or there are beings that are
out there in our universe who

00:42:58.220 --> 00:43:00.410 align:middle line:90%
have already accomplished this.

00:43:00.410 --> 00:43:04.310 align:middle line:84%
And they are looking for
you and me to assist us

00:43:04.310 --> 00:43:07.580 align:middle line:90%
in completing our ascension.

00:43:07.580 --> 00:43:10.520 align:middle line:84%
I don't have to write the
book on the rainbow light body

00:43:10.520 --> 00:43:12.110 align:middle line:90%
within every detail.

00:43:12.110 --> 00:43:16.970 align:middle line:84%
These beings who have already
done it are the experts at it.

00:43:16.970 --> 00:43:18.950 align:middle line:84%
And they're out
there looking for us.

00:43:18.950 --> 00:43:20.380 align:middle line:90%
It's like we're the--

00:43:20.380 --> 00:43:22.343 align:middle line:90%
we got our light bulbs up here.

00:43:22.343 --> 00:43:24.260 align:middle line:84%
And for the most part,
none of our light bulbs

00:43:24.260 --> 00:43:26.630 align:middle line:90%
are screwed in, right?

00:43:26.630 --> 00:43:29.085 align:middle line:84%
But some of us have been
screwing in the light bulb.

00:43:29.085 --> 00:43:31.460 align:middle line:84%
And we're about to rake up
enough energy within ourselves

00:43:31.460 --> 00:43:32.900 align:middle line:90%
where, bing.

00:43:32.900 --> 00:43:34.430 align:middle line:90%
The light lights up.

00:43:34.430 --> 00:43:36.020 align:middle line:84%
That's when the
rainbow angels come in

00:43:36.020 --> 00:43:38.600 align:middle line:90%
and say, OK, put out your hand.

00:43:38.600 --> 00:43:41.480 align:middle line:84%
Literally putting
the-- completing

00:43:41.480 --> 00:43:44.460 align:middle line:84%
the secrets of ascension
in the palm of our hand.

00:43:44.460 --> 00:43:48.560 align:middle line:84%
That story is repeated over
and over and over again

00:43:48.560 --> 00:43:52.670 align:middle line:84%
in ascension stories, that
the person in the story--

00:43:52.670 --> 00:43:56.040 align:middle line:84%
Enoch, for example--
pre-flood scholar,

00:43:56.040 --> 00:43:58.560 align:middle line:84%
was just like you and I,
attended a lot of seminars,

00:43:58.560 --> 00:43:59.360 align:middle line:90%
went to--

00:43:59.360 --> 00:44:02.600 align:middle line:84%
watched ancient aliens
or did all this work

00:44:02.600 --> 00:44:03.950 align:middle line:90%
and has pieced it all together.

00:44:03.950 --> 00:44:05.920 align:middle line:90%
It's like, oh, bing.

00:44:05.920 --> 00:44:07.550 align:middle line:90%
I'm screwing my light bulb in.

00:44:07.550 --> 00:44:10.400 align:middle line:10%
And then all of a sudden,
the Archangel Michael

00:44:10.400 --> 00:44:13.085 align:middle line:10%
appears and says, OK,
Enoch, you've hit the books.

00:44:13.085 --> 00:44:14.960 align:middle line:84%
You know enough where
I'm not going to-- it's

00:44:14.960 --> 00:44:16.335 align:middle line:84%
not going to be
dangerous for you

00:44:16.335 --> 00:44:18.350 align:middle line:84%
or harmful for you to
go on this journey.

00:44:18.350 --> 00:44:20.990 align:middle line:84%
Michael takes him up
through several heavens.

00:44:20.990 --> 00:44:22.790 align:middle line:84%
They take him up to
the third heaven, which

00:44:22.790 --> 00:44:27.230 align:middle line:84%
could be another dimension--
anoints Enoch's body with oil

00:44:27.230 --> 00:44:29.180 align:middle line:84%
so that now Enoch's
body in the story

00:44:29.180 --> 00:44:31.490 align:middle line:84%
dissolves into
rainbow-colored light,

00:44:31.490 --> 00:44:35.000 align:middle line:84%
so that his body matches
that of the angels.

00:44:35.000 --> 00:44:36.110 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:44:36.110 --> 00:44:40.700 align:middle line:84%
You mean there's an oil that can
transmute our body into light?

00:44:40.700 --> 00:44:42.660 align:middle line:84%
Call Gary Young
and Young Living.

00:44:42.660 --> 00:44:43.460 align:middle line:90%
Let's get on this.

00:44:43.460 --> 00:44:45.090 align:middle line:84%
Let's start making
this oil right now.

00:44:45.090 --> 00:44:46.760 align:middle line:84%
Because I love
your Thieves drops.

00:44:46.760 --> 00:44:47.960 align:middle line:90%
I drink it by the gallon.

00:44:47.960 --> 00:44:49.710 align:middle line:84%
I love everything, but
what we really need

00:44:49.710 --> 00:44:51.920 align:middle line:90%
is a resurrection oil, right?

00:44:51.920 --> 00:44:52.880 align:middle line:90%
Where do you get that?

00:44:52.880 --> 00:44:54.730 align:middle line:90%
>> [INAUDIBLE] process.

00:44:54.730 --> 00:44:55.530 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, yeah.

00:44:55.530 --> 00:44:58.560 align:middle line:84%
And Gary is in his
rainbow body now.

00:44:58.560 --> 00:45:00.020 align:middle line:90%
He's probably laughing at me.

00:45:00.020 --> 00:45:03.650 align:middle line:84%
But the point is, is
that in these stories,

00:45:03.650 --> 00:45:06.980 align:middle line:84%
they tell us how it's done,
and that we're never alone

00:45:06.980 --> 00:45:08.320 align:middle line:90%
on this path.

00:45:08.320 --> 00:45:10.820 align:middle line:84%
And so what then happens, of
course, to finish Enoch's story

00:45:10.820 --> 00:45:13.100 align:middle line:90%
is he goes up to heaven.

00:45:13.100 --> 00:45:15.178 align:middle line:84%
And God talks with him
and says, oh, yeah.

00:45:15.178 --> 00:45:16.970 align:middle line:84%
Why don't you hang
around for a little bit?

00:45:16.970 --> 00:45:17.870 align:middle line:90%
I'll give you a job.

00:45:17.870 --> 00:45:18.670 align:middle line:90%
I know.

00:45:18.670 --> 00:45:20.610 align:middle line:90%
You'll be a janitor.

00:45:20.610 --> 00:45:23.120 align:middle line:84%
You sweep up around
the throne, Enoch.

00:45:23.120 --> 00:45:25.200 align:middle line:84%
And that's Enoch does
for about 30 days

00:45:25.200 --> 00:45:26.950 align:middle line:90%
while he's educated as well.

00:45:26.950 --> 00:45:28.567 align:middle line:84%
Then it's time for
him to come back.

00:45:28.567 --> 00:45:30.400 align:middle line:84%
And people think, oh,
that's a terrible job.

00:45:30.400 --> 00:45:33.780 align:middle line:84%
Who wants to be a janitor
at the throne of God?

00:45:33.780 --> 00:45:35.350 align:middle line:90%
I do.

00:45:35.350 --> 00:45:36.150 align:middle line:90%
I do.

00:45:36.150 --> 00:45:37.125 align:middle line:90%
How do I apply?

00:45:37.125 --> 00:45:37.925 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:45:37.925 --> 00:45:39.840 align:middle line:84%
And so Enoch comes
back to Earth.

00:45:39.840 --> 00:45:42.370 align:middle line:90%
Then he's taken back up again.

00:45:42.370 --> 00:45:45.540 align:middle line:84%
And now, he's given a
new name and a new job.

00:45:45.540 --> 00:45:47.620 align:middle line:90%
His new name is Metatron.

00:45:47.620 --> 00:45:50.310 align:middle line:84%
And his new job
is he's the guide.

00:45:50.310 --> 00:45:53.250 align:middle line:84%
It's Metatron who's
looking for you.

00:45:53.250 --> 00:45:54.060 align:middle line:90%
He's way up.

00:45:54.060 --> 00:45:55.280 align:middle line:90%
I just saw that bulb.

00:45:55.280 --> 00:45:57.990 align:middle line:84%
He got that little more
twist there and up it goes.

00:45:57.990 --> 00:46:02.110 align:middle line:84%
And you're going to-- yeah,
they're looking for us.

00:46:02.110 --> 00:46:04.890 align:middle line:84%
And so we're going to reach
up to them, just as they're

00:46:04.890 --> 00:46:07.020 align:middle line:84%
going to come down
to us and assist us

00:46:07.020 --> 00:46:09.210 align:middle line:90%
in completing our ascension.

00:46:09.210 --> 00:46:11.010 align:middle line:84%
This teaching-- and
it was the Essenes

00:46:11.010 --> 00:46:12.780 align:middle line:90%
who wrote the story of Enoch.

00:46:12.780 --> 00:46:16.170 align:middle line:84%
This was another one of
their rewire the brain

00:46:16.170 --> 00:46:18.120 align:middle line:90%
visualization techniques.

00:46:18.120 --> 00:46:22.080 align:middle line:84%
Over and over again, they would
rehearse this story of Enoch

00:46:22.080 --> 00:46:23.670 align:middle line:90%
going up and being transformed.

00:46:23.670 --> 00:46:27.030 align:middle line:84%
What would it feel like to have
that oil running down your body

00:46:27.030 --> 00:46:29.380 align:middle line:84%
and your body dissolving
into rainbow-colored light,

00:46:29.380 --> 00:46:31.150 align:middle line:90%
so you're just like the angels?

00:46:31.150 --> 00:46:31.980 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:46:31.980 --> 00:46:35.070 align:middle line:84%
They'd rehearse, rehearse,
rehearse, rehearse this

00:46:35.070 --> 00:46:39.270 align:middle line:84%
until it was a physical
reality within their own body.

00:46:39.270 --> 00:46:41.400 align:middle line:10%
This teaching is referred
to in the "Dead Sea

00:46:41.400 --> 00:46:44.670 align:middle line:10%
Scrolls" as the perfect
way, perfection of holiness,

00:46:44.670 --> 00:46:48.000 align:middle line:10%
perfect holiness, walking
in the way of perfection.

00:46:48.000 --> 00:46:51.630 align:middle line:10%
And it was given to the Essenes
by these other worldly beings

00:46:51.630 --> 00:46:53.280 align:middle line:10%
who were referred
to in the scrolls

00:46:53.280 --> 00:46:55.770 align:middle line:10%
as the heavenly holy
ones, sons of heaven,

00:46:55.770 --> 00:46:59.820 align:middle line:10%
holy angels of the
Lord, or perfect ones.

00:46:59.820 --> 00:47:01.710 align:middle line:84%
Why are they called
the perfect ones?

00:47:01.710 --> 00:47:04.950 align:middle line:84%
Well, because they're in
their rainbow light body,

00:47:04.950 --> 00:47:07.500 align:middle line:90%
their perfect light body.

00:47:07.500 --> 00:47:10.920 align:middle line:84%
And that is the goal
of human evolution

00:47:10.920 --> 00:47:13.740 align:middle line:84%
is for us to transform
our planet into a planet

00:47:13.740 --> 00:47:15.900 align:middle line:90%
of holiness and righteousness.

00:47:15.900 --> 00:47:19.030 align:middle line:84%
Atlantis tried
and failed, right?

00:47:19.030 --> 00:47:19.960 align:middle line:90%
Remember that?

00:47:19.960 --> 00:47:20.760 align:middle line:90%
That whole story?

00:47:20.760 --> 00:47:22.390 align:middle line:84%
The Atlanteans,
according to Plato,

00:47:22.390 --> 00:47:24.700 align:middle line:90%
were hybrids of the gods.

00:47:24.700 --> 00:47:26.602 align:middle line:84%
They had a divine
element within them.

00:47:26.602 --> 00:47:28.060 align:middle line:84%
But then they
started to ignore it.

00:47:28.060 --> 00:47:30.190 align:middle line:84%
They behaved
righteously for a while.

00:47:30.190 --> 00:47:32.380 align:middle line:10%
Then they said, oh, we
knew that-- oh, that

00:47:32.380 --> 00:47:33.285 align:middle line:10%
righteousness crap.

00:47:33.285 --> 00:47:34.085 align:middle line:90%
I won't come out.

00:47:34.085 --> 00:47:36.190 align:middle line:84%
It's much more fun
to be naughty, right?

00:47:36.190 --> 00:47:37.960 align:middle line:84%
Then that's what
they started to do.

00:47:37.960 --> 00:47:40.060 align:middle line:90%
And that divine element faded.

00:47:40.060 --> 00:47:41.950 align:middle line:84%
Zeus is watching
from high above.

00:47:41.950 --> 00:47:45.850 align:middle line:84%
And he goes, OK,
here's the flood.

00:47:45.850 --> 00:47:46.880 align:middle line:90%
See you all later.

00:47:46.880 --> 00:47:47.680 align:middle line:90%
You blew it.

00:47:47.680 --> 00:47:50.620 align:middle line:84%
That's the story
of Atlantis, right?

00:47:50.620 --> 00:47:54.340 align:middle line:84%
The key story or key aspect
of the Atlantean mythos

00:47:54.340 --> 00:47:57.610 align:middle line:84%
is they lost touch with
their divine element

00:47:57.610 --> 00:48:00.220 align:middle line:90%
and their righteous true selves.

00:48:00.220 --> 00:48:03.890 align:middle line:84%
And an entity, Zeus,
said enough's enough.

