It's such a powerful painting.

01:07:12.280 --> 01:07:16.830 align:middle line:84%
And just imagine we're in a
room that's just candle lit.

01:07:16.830 --> 01:07:19.320 align:middle line:84%
And this haunting
image is just floating

01:07:19.320 --> 01:07:22.830 align:middle line:84%
in the room in front of us,
offering to us the Chintamani.

01:07:22.830 --> 01:07:24.750 align:middle line:90%
That's the way I view this.

01:07:24.750 --> 01:07:27.330 align:middle line:84%
And that's how it would
have originally been viewed.

01:07:27.330 --> 01:07:28.860 align:middle line:90%
Just so profound.

01:07:28.860 --> 01:07:30.780 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, we
know for sure this

01:07:30.780 --> 01:07:33.390 align:middle line:84%
is Christ, because it's
the exact same face

01:07:33.390 --> 01:07:35.460 align:middle line:90%
on the Shroud of Turin.

01:07:35.460 --> 01:07:37.870 align:middle line:84%
And so please don't tell
