01:07:37.870 --> 01:07:39.180 align:middle line:90%
Don't give me that crap.

01:07:39.180 --> 01:07:41.040 align:middle line:90%
That is such a bogus argument.

01:07:41.040 --> 01:07:42.120 align:middle line:90%
Of course, he did.

01:07:42.120 --> 01:07:46.500 align:middle line:84%
And of course, the Shroud
of Turin is an icon.

01:07:46.500 --> 01:07:49.680 align:middle line:84%
It's an icon, as the Catholic
Church has now affirmed,

01:07:49.680 --> 01:07:52.200 align:middle line:84%
of Christ and his
resurrection body.

01:07:52.200 --> 01:07:54.990 align:middle line:90%
The face is identical.

01:07:54.990 --> 01:07:56.570 align:middle line:90%
It's identical.

01:07:56.570 --> 01:08:00.110 align:middle line:84%
And Leonardo never saw
the Shroud of Turin.

01:08:00.110 --> 01:08:02.570 align:middle line:90%
So here we are.

01:08:02.570 --> 01:08:07.190 align:middle line:10%
How is it possible for an
image to transmit the presence

01:08:07.190 --> 01:08:08.612 align:middle line:10%
or vibration of a deity?

01:08:08.612 --> 01:08:10.820 align:middle line:84%
Let's get into the neuroscience
of this a little bit.

01:08:10.820 --> 01:08:13.190 align:middle line:90%
It's very, very interesting.

01:08:13.190 --> 01:08:16.760 align:middle line:84%
Around 200,000 years ago,
some mysterious event

01:08:16.760 --> 01:08:20.660 align:middle line:84%
occurred that spontaneously
led to the modern human brain

01:08:20.660 --> 01:08:23.270 align:middle line:90%
coming into existence in Africa.

01:08:23.270 --> 01:08:25.010 align:middle line:84%
And this is what
Michelangelo is trying

01:08:25.010 --> 01:08:27.500 align:middle line:84%
to capture in this painting
in the Sistine Chapel

01:08:27.500 --> 01:08:28.979 align:middle line:90%
of the creation of man.

01:08:28.979 --> 01:08:33.080 align:middle line:84%
Here's God transmitting
something to Adam

01:08:33.080 --> 01:08:34.580 align:middle line:90%
who's over here on the left.

01:08:34.580 --> 01:08:36.620 align:middle line:10%
Now, something you
need to know here

01:08:36.620 --> 01:08:41.510 align:middle line:10%
is that Adam is portrayed as a
young man in the perfect body

01:08:41.510 --> 01:08:42.770 align:middle line:10%
of a Greek athlete.

01:08:42.770 --> 01:08:46.880 align:middle line:10%
This is how the Greeks visualize
the perfect light body.

01:08:46.880 --> 01:08:49.130 align:middle line:10%
This isn't actually
some Greek stud

01:08:49.130 --> 01:08:51.590 align:middle line:10%
we're looking at
with a six pack.

01:08:51.590 --> 01:08:54.710 align:middle line:84%
This is how the perfect
proportions of this body

01:08:54.710 --> 01:08:58.430 align:middle line:84%
are reflective of the perfect
proportions of the light body.

01:08:58.430 --> 01:09:01.399 align:middle line:84%
And so because
Adam in this moment

01:09:01.399 --> 01:09:04.069 align:middle line:84%
is not in his flesh
and blood body.

01:09:04.069 --> 01:09:08.300 align:middle line:84%
He is in the moment
before the so-called fall

01:09:08.300 --> 01:09:10.520 align:middle line:84%
in the Book of Genesis
when all of humanity

01:09:10.520 --> 01:09:13.490 align:middle line:90%
was in a light body form.

01:09:13.490 --> 01:09:15.380 align:middle line:10%
And so he is in his
light body being

01:09:15.380 --> 01:09:18.649 align:middle line:10%
prepared to receive an
infusion of something that

01:09:18.649 --> 01:09:20.660 align:middle line:10%
would transform him.

01:09:20.660 --> 01:09:23.359 align:middle line:10%
As the book of Zohar says,
the Jewish mystical book,

01:09:23.359 --> 01:09:25.050 align:middle line:10%
when Adam dwelt in
the Garden of Eden,

01:09:25.050 --> 01:09:27.680 align:middle line:10%
he was clothed in the
celestial garment, which is

01:09:27.680 --> 01:09:29.720 align:middle line:10%
the garment of heavenly light.

01:09:29.720 --> 01:09:31.370 align:middle line:10%
That's exactly what
the Buddhas teach.

01:09:31.370 --> 01:09:35.609 align:middle line:10%
This is our true
nature as light beings.

01:09:35.609 --> 01:09:38.359 align:middle line:84%
And so in the Church of St.
Francis of Assisi in Assisi,

01:09:38.359 --> 01:09:42.380 align:middle line:10%
Italy, we see
Christ, God creating

01:09:42.380 --> 01:09:46.340 align:middle line:10%
Adam as a being of
light in a mandorla,

01:09:46.340 --> 01:09:48.439 align:middle line:10%
a perfect gateway of light.

01:09:48.439 --> 01:09:50.870 align:middle line:10%
Beyond our material
and emotional body,

01:09:50.870 --> 01:09:54.770 align:middle line:10%
we have a body of light,
says Christian mysticism.

01:09:54.770 --> 01:09:58.430 align:middle line:84%
Deep, deep inside of us, there
is a pure being, a pure light,

01:09:58.430 --> 01:10:02.300 align:middle line:84%
pure energy existing
and total potentiality

01:10:02.300 --> 01:10:04.550 align:middle line:90%
and then came the fall.

01:10:04.550 --> 01:10:07.610 align:middle line:10%
And what this means is that
humans, when we lived in Eden,

01:10:07.610 --> 01:10:09.290 align:middle line:10%
were in a different form.

01:10:09.290 --> 01:10:12.080 align:middle line:10%
We had perfect bodies of light.

01:10:12.080 --> 01:10:14.240 align:middle line:10%
And all of human
history is a quest

01:10:14.240 --> 01:10:20.090 align:middle line:10%
to get back to our original
status as pure light beings.

01:10:20.090 --> 01:10:22.040 align:middle line:10%
The Kabbalistic theory
of humanity's origins

01:10:22.040 --> 01:10:24.440 align:middle line:10%
as light beings is
echoed in Paul's comments

01:10:24.440 --> 01:10:27.890 align:middle line:10%
in Corinthians when he said,
God created a heavenly atom

01:10:27.890 --> 01:10:31.490 align:middle line:10%
in the spiritual world and
an earthly atom of clay

01:10:31.490 --> 01:10:33.417 align:middle line:10%
for the material world.

01:10:33.417 --> 01:10:35.000 align:middle line:84%
Remember the Buddhist
image of the guy

01:10:35.000 --> 01:10:37.470 align:middle line:84%
in his earthly body connected
through the rainbow bridge

01:10:37.470 --> 01:10:38.330 align:middle line:90%
to his rainbow body?

01:10:38.330 --> 01:10:39.860 align:middle line:90%
Exact same teaching.

01:10:39.860 --> 01:10:42.080 align:middle line:90%
Exact same teaching.

01:10:42.080 --> 01:10:46.460 align:middle line:84%
We have our earthly self, and
we have our celestial self.

01:10:46.460 --> 01:10:48.740 align:middle line:84%
And we're trying to
get back to that state

01:10:48.740 --> 01:10:52.040 align:middle line:84%
where they're unified and we are
in our perfect bodies of light.

01:10:52.040 --> 01:10:54.710 align:middle line:10%
The Gospel of Philip
is a gnostic gospel

01:10:54.710 --> 01:10:56.510 align:middle line:10%
that informs us about
this, telling us

01:10:56.510 --> 01:10:58.400 align:middle line:10%
the Lord rose from the dead.

01:10:58.400 --> 01:11:00.080 align:middle line:10%
He became as he was.

01:11:00.080 --> 01:11:03.350 align:middle line:10%
But now, his body was perfect.

01:11:03.350 --> 01:11:04.940 align:middle line:10%
And how many times
have we dropped

01:11:04.940 --> 01:11:07.490 align:middle line:10%
the word perfect in
our conversation today?

01:11:07.490 --> 01:11:08.690 align:middle line:90%
Multiple times.

01:11:08.690 --> 01:11:10.640 align:middle line:84%
Because it is the
key word that we

01:11:10.640 --> 01:11:12.680 align:middle line:84%
can use to weave ourselves
through these rainbow

01:11:12.680 --> 01:11:14.270 align:middle line:90%
light body traditions.

01:11:14.270 --> 01:11:17.720 align:middle line:10%
He possessed flesh, but
this was true flesh.

01:11:17.720 --> 01:11:20.000 align:middle line:10%
Our flesh isn't true.

01:11:20.000 --> 01:11:24.050 align:middle line:10%
Our flesh is only an
image of the true.

01:11:24.050 --> 01:11:27.890 align:middle line:84%
Oh, so we're made
in the image of God.

01:11:27.890 --> 01:11:30.890 align:middle line:84%
God is not some dirty, old
white man on the throne.

01:11:30.890 --> 01:11:33.680 align:middle line:84%
That's not the image
we're talking about.

01:11:33.680 --> 01:11:37.640 align:middle line:84%
We are made in the image of God
in terms of our rainbow light

01:11:37.640 --> 01:11:38.870 align:middle line:90%
body.

01:11:38.870 --> 01:11:41.960 align:middle line:10%
When we get that, it
opens up a whole new way

01:11:41.960 --> 01:11:43.710 align:middle line:10%
of looking at this.

01:11:43.710 --> 01:11:45.650 align:middle line:84%
So the question
then is, how do we

01:11:45.650 --> 01:11:49.010 align:middle line:84%
get back to our original
rainbow light body?

01:11:49.010 --> 01:11:50.600 align:middle line:10%
Well, we follow this path.

01:11:50.600 --> 01:11:53.480 align:middle line:10%
So God created mankind
in his own image.

01:11:53.480 --> 01:11:56.390 align:middle line:10%
In the image of God, he
created them-- male and female.

01:11:56.390 --> 01:11:58.790 align:middle line:10%
He created them.

01:11:58.790 --> 01:12:01.660 align:middle line:90%
God is a artist.

01:12:01.660 --> 01:12:04.410 align:middle line:90%
We're an artistic creation.

01:12:04.410 --> 01:12:06.220 align:middle line:90%
We're works of art.

01:12:06.220 --> 01:12:10.030 align:middle line:84%
We're images made in the
image of our creator.

01:12:10.030 --> 01:12:15.810 align:middle line:84%
We are icons of
artistic parents, right?

01:12:15.810 --> 01:12:18.780 align:middle line:84%
What is the light spirit, then,
that they transmitted to us?

01:12:18.780 --> 01:12:22.020 align:middle line:84%
When God is reaching out to
Adam to zap something to him,

01:12:22.020 --> 01:12:24.800 align:middle line:84%
what is that, that
he was transmitting?

01:12:24.800 --> 01:12:29.010 align:middle line:84%
Well, the answer is
it's the Holy Spirit.

01:12:29.010 --> 01:12:31.450 align:middle line:10%
We'll come to that
in just a moment.

01:12:31.450 --> 01:12:33.818 align:middle line:10%
This image is from the
13th century in France.

01:12:33.818 --> 01:12:35.610 align:middle line:10%
And I'm going to go
back just for a moment.

01:12:35.610 --> 01:12:36.960 align:middle line:10%
You see God there?

01:12:36.960 --> 01:12:39.570 align:middle line:10%
He's got a compass in his hand.

01:12:39.570 --> 01:12:42.600 align:middle line:10%
This is the first time
humanity is starting to think

01:12:42.600 --> 01:12:45.900 align:middle line:10%
technology is a gift from God.

01:12:45.900 --> 01:12:49.020 align:middle line:10%
So they actually started to
portray God with technology

01:12:49.020 --> 01:12:50.040 align:middle line:10%
in his hands.

01:12:50.040 --> 01:12:51.555 align:middle line:10%
Tools, right?

01:12:51.555 --> 01:12:53.610 align:middle line:10%
In this case, a compass.

01:12:53.610 --> 01:12:57.930 align:middle line:10%
And God is using that
compass to manipulate

01:12:57.930 --> 01:13:01.950 align:middle line:10%
the image of humanity,
which is readily

01:13:01.950 --> 01:13:05.580 align:middle line:10%
identifiable as a fractal.

01:13:05.580 --> 01:13:07.350 align:middle line:90%
In fact, it's a Mandelbrot set.

01:13:07.350 --> 01:13:11.400 align:middle line:84%
So here's the image
from the 13th century.

01:13:11.400 --> 01:13:13.800 align:middle line:90%
There's the Mandelbrot set.

01:13:13.800 --> 01:13:15.600 align:middle line:90%
It's the exact same image.

01:13:15.600 --> 01:13:18.060 align:middle line:84%
It's the exact
same thing, right?

01:13:18.060 --> 01:13:20.310 align:middle line:84%
The Mandelbrot set
was discovered in 1980

01:13:20.310 --> 01:13:23.640 align:middle line:84%
by Benoit Mandelbrot who was
working at IBM at the time.

01:13:23.640 --> 01:13:26.040 align:middle line:84%
It's an infinitely
complex geometrical shape

01:13:26.040 --> 01:13:28.650 align:middle line:84%
called the Mandelbrot set that
uses a very simple equation

01:13:28.650 --> 01:13:30.390 align:middle line:90%
with computers and graphics.

01:13:30.390 --> 01:13:33.570 align:middle line:84%
It was only possible to create
that image with the invention

01:13:33.570 --> 01:13:35.820 align:middle line:90%
of computers.

01:13:35.820 --> 01:13:38.850 align:middle line:84%
Without computers, we're not
getting the Mandelbrot set.

01:13:38.850 --> 01:13:40.680 align:middle line:84%
And the Mandelbrot
set is generated

01:13:40.680 --> 01:13:43.140 align:middle line:84%
by what is called iteration,
which means to repeat

01:13:43.140 --> 01:13:45.790 align:middle line:90%
a process over and over again.

01:13:45.790 --> 01:13:47.130 align:middle line:90%
It's a set of numbers.

01:13:47.130 --> 01:13:49.510 align:middle line:84%
And from these numbers,
you can generate pictures.

01:13:49.510 --> 01:13:52.320 align:middle line:10%
And the pictures are
infinitely complicated.

01:13:52.320 --> 01:13:55.140 align:middle line:10%
At every level of
magnification, the pattern

01:13:55.140 --> 01:13:58.110 align:middle line:10%
repeats itself into infinity.

01:13:58.110 --> 01:14:00.690 align:middle line:10%
They call it a mathematical
icon that they refer

01:14:00.690 --> 01:14:02.940 align:middle line:10%
to as the thumbprint of God.

01:14:02.940 --> 01:14:05.380 align:middle line:10%
So here's an image of
the Mandelbrot set.

01:14:05.380 --> 01:14:08.040 align:middle line:10%
And no matter how many
times or how deeply you

01:14:08.040 --> 01:14:11.280 align:middle line:10%
magnify that image
at every level,

01:14:11.280 --> 01:14:15.190 align:middle line:10%
it stays exactly the same.

01:14:15.190 --> 01:14:16.990 align:middle line:84%
We're made in the
image of God, so we

01:14:16.990 --> 01:14:20.620 align:middle line:84%
are fractals of
God, which means we

01:14:20.620 --> 01:14:22.690 align:middle line:84%
contain all of God's
essence within us

01:14:22.690 --> 01:14:26.030 align:middle line:90%
and capabilities as fractals.

01:14:26.030 --> 01:14:26.830 align:middle line:90%
Here's the thing.

01:14:26.830 --> 01:14:29.200 align:middle line:84%
If a programmer looks
at the Mandelbrot set

01:14:29.200 --> 01:14:31.720 align:middle line:84%
and wants to change
some tiny detail,

01:14:31.720 --> 01:14:34.780 align:middle line:84%
make another curlicue
or a bump go away,

01:14:34.780 --> 01:14:36.640 align:middle line:84%
they can't do it
without going back

01:14:36.640 --> 01:14:39.930 align:middle line:84%
to the original creation
or original equation

01:14:39.930 --> 01:14:42.470 align:middle line:90%
and starting all over again.

01:14:42.470 --> 01:14:45.100 align:middle line:10%
So in effect, they tear
down the universe in order

01:14:45.100 --> 01:14:47.560 align:middle line:10%
to augment or build a new one.

01:14:47.560 --> 01:14:50.800 align:middle line:10%
Within this Mandelbrot set, we
see the richness of our unity

01:14:50.800 --> 01:14:53.110 align:middle line:10%
and also the richness
of our individuality.

01:14:53.110 --> 01:14:57.010 align:middle line:84%
We are baby Mandelbrot
sets or fractals.

01:14:57.010 --> 01:14:59.590 align:middle line:84%
Now, some clever
mathematician back in the '80s

01:14:59.590 --> 01:15:00.700 align:middle line:90%
said, wow, Ben.

01:15:00.700 --> 01:15:02.830 align:middle line:90%
Wow, that is really awesome.

01:15:02.830 --> 01:15:08.140 align:middle line:84%
And what I see in the Mandelbrot
set is a meditating Buddha.

01:15:08.140 --> 01:15:11.260 align:middle line:10%
So here's the Akasagarbha
Buddha holding the triple dots

01:15:11.260 --> 01:15:13.330 align:middle line:10%
of the Chintamani, the
wish-fulfilling gem

01:15:13.330 --> 01:15:14.950 align:middle line:10%
at the level of
the heart that can

01:15:14.950 --> 01:15:16.840 align:middle line:10%
transmute the body into light.

01:15:16.840 --> 01:15:18.670 align:middle line:10%
And what I'm going to
do is take that image

01:15:18.670 --> 01:15:23.160 align:middle line:10%
and superimpose on it
the Mandelbrot set.

01:15:23.160 --> 01:15:24.510 align:middle line:90%
It's a perfect match.

01:15:24.510 --> 01:15:26.250 align:middle line:84%
I don't even have
Photoshop, so I didn't

01:15:26.250 --> 01:15:27.550 align:middle line:90%
manipulate this in any way.

01:15:27.550 --> 01:15:28.370 align:middle line:90%
I just went, doink.

01:15:28.370 --> 01:15:29.430 align:middle line:90%
And there it is.

01:15:29.430 --> 01:15:31.440 align:middle line:90%
Perfect match.

01:15:31.440 --> 01:15:33.720 align:middle line:84%
So what the mathematicians
decided to do--

01:15:33.720 --> 01:15:35.670 align:middle line:90%
let's change the equation.

01:15:35.670 --> 01:15:39.810 align:middle line:84%
And they came up with what they
call the Buddhabrot, right?

01:15:39.810 --> 01:15:42.950 align:middle line:84%
And I'm sitting at my desk,
looking at this going,

01:15:42.950 --> 01:15:45.690 align:middle line:90%
a rainbow-colored Buddhabrot.

01:15:45.690 --> 01:15:49.450 align:middle line:84%
What do you suppose is
going through my mind?

01:15:49.450 --> 01:15:52.630 align:middle line:84%
It's a perfect match for
Padmasambhava in the rainbow

01:15:52.630 --> 01:15:54.070 align:middle line:90%
body.

01:15:54.070 --> 01:15:56.490 align:middle line:84%
Ding, ding, ding, ding,
ding, ding, ding, ding, ding.

01:15:56.490 --> 01:15:57.910 align:middle line:90%
There's more confirmation.

01:15:57.910 --> 01:15:59.890 align:middle line:84%
The rainbow body
is our true nature.

01:15:59.890 --> 01:16:01.840 align:middle line:90%
We are made in the image of God.

01:16:01.840 --> 01:16:03.790 align:middle line:84%
It's not some dirty, old
white man on a throne

01:16:03.790 --> 01:16:05.790 align:middle line:84%
that everybody hates and
doesn't want me to talk

01:16:05.790 --> 01:16:08.830 align:middle line:90%
about religion anywhere.

01:16:08.830 --> 01:16:13.060 align:middle line:84%
It's the light body, is the
image we're talking about.

01:16:13.060 --> 01:16:16.840 align:middle line:10%
It's the light body that
we're made in the image of.

01:16:16.840 --> 01:16:19.210 align:middle line:10%
Christianity teaches this.

01:16:19.210 --> 01:16:22.690 align:middle line:10%
Because humans are made in
the perfect image of God,

01:16:22.690 --> 01:16:27.790 align:middle line:10%
we have the spiritual capacity
to participate in or mirror

01:16:27.790 --> 01:16:30.430 align:middle line:10%
Jesus's divine glory
as image bearers

01:16:30.430 --> 01:16:33.370 align:middle line:10%
and reactivate our light bodies.

01:16:33.370 --> 01:16:36.580 align:middle line:10%
The Bible is very
direct and specific.

01:16:36.580 --> 01:16:40.480 align:middle line:10%
As was the man of
dust or DNA, clay,

01:16:40.480 --> 01:16:44.590 align:middle line:10%
so also are those of dust
as is the man of heaven,

01:16:44.590 --> 01:16:47.020 align:middle line:10%
so also are those
who are of heaven.

01:16:47.020 --> 01:16:47.990 align:middle line:90%
Here it is.

01:16:47.990 --> 01:16:51.040 align:middle line:10%
Just as we have born the
image of the man of dust,

01:16:51.040 --> 01:16:54.820 align:middle line:10%
our earthly flesh and
blood bodies, so also shall

01:16:54.820 --> 01:16:58.610 align:middle line:10%
we bear the image of
the man of heaven.

01:16:58.610 --> 01:17:01.420 align:middle line:10%
It's already within us.

01:17:01.420 --> 01:17:05.590 align:middle line:10%
The image of the man of heaven
is Jesus in his rainbow light

